{"id":314632,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-维权访民赵云侠、初东芳拘留期满表示会/","date":"2013-09-22T08:34:54Z","modified":"2013-09-22T08:34:54Z","title":"维权网 | 维权访民赵云侠、初东芳拘留期满表示会继续维权（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日，赵云侠、初东芳在府右街北口以爬树锁身，喊冤并打横幅、撒传单的方式抗议司法腐败。赵云侠、初东芳分别被以“扰乱公共场所秩序”行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。两人于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日拘留期满后获释。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>两人获得自由见面后悲喜交加。赵云侠说：“每逢佳节倍思亲，自从儿子见义勇为，离开我们就再也没有过过节。她对自己的儿子说：“妈妈失去了你很痛心、很痛心，但更让妈妈痛心的是公安局的不作为、法院的枉法判决，儿子妈妈失去了你，但妈妈绝不失去对正义的追求。儿子，你不该离开妈妈，你走了，走的那么突然</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">…… 9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日法院开庭重审这起案件了，我们等待法院的审判结果。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>初东芳则说：“今年的中秋节还是在拘留所里度过。十多年来我的上访生涯告诉我，维权是第一需要。哥哥被错判入狱，我手拿司法机关的笔记鉴定，证明哥哥初少才在公安局做的笔录不是本人签字，可公检法至今不给我任何答复。哥哥在监狱里，家已不像家了，过节就没法想了。面对司法腐败，我无法容忍，无论我用什么办法，就是为了和司法腐败抗争，就是为了争取我们的权利”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>两人一再表示：不管前面的路多艰难，但一定会维权到底。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8WNSkDSxX_A/Uj6TpjOChnI/AAAAAAAAoeI/MqWd2M-8e4I/s1600/2013-.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8WNSkDSxX_A/Uj6TpjOChnI/AAAAAAAAoeI/MqWd2M-8e4I/s320/2013-.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ecWy9yQBCwE/Uj6Tu250ImI/AAAAAAAAoeY/kvb6rEgSlBo/s1600/%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%A4%84%E7%BD%9A%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A601.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ecWy9yQBCwE/Uj6Tu250ImI/AAAAAAAAoeY/kvb6rEgSlBo/s320/%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%A4%84%E7%BD%9A%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A601.jpg\" width=\"238\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-gY8v5k3JnJc/Uj6TtBnxrVI/AAAAAAAAoeU/b-8Zd7mxlpw/s1600/%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A4%2584%25E7%25BD%259A%25E5%2586%25B3%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B9%25A602.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-gY8v5k3JnJc/Uj6TtBnxrVI/AAAAAAAAoeU/b-8Zd7mxlpw/s320/%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A4%2584%25E7%25BD%259A%25E5%2586%25B3%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B9%25A602.jpg\" width=\"236\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}